results.title: Dark Judgment Part 1
results.description: While in the midsts of a gang war between rival crime bosses, The Punisher searches for a serial killer and tries to make a connection between them.

results.title: [Countdown: 2] Dead and Deader
results.description: Punisher and Cruz try to fight each other while engaging in a running battle with the mob; Bullseye, in Mather's armor, takes care of some mob business; Taking advantage of the chaos being wrought by the Punisher, Kingpin decides to try and reclaim his old position in crime; Stone Cold kills Cruz; During a shootout in the park with gangsters, Punisher accidentally kills a family on a picnic and, deciding his war is over, walks into the police station to turn himself in.

results.title: Begin the Future History of Spider-Man 2099
results.description: Miguel O'Hara, hot-shot geneticist, tries to quit his job at Alchemax but is addicted to a drug by his boss, Tyler Stone. In an effort to free himself of the addiction, his genetic code is merged with a spider's genetic code.

results.title: Mother's Day
results.description: Miguel, Dana, and Gabriel visit Mrs. O'Hara, and she fakes death to get a rise out of Miguel.  In a flashback we learn that Miguel was sent to an Alchemax training school by his father.  We also learn that he hates his now deceased father.

results.title: Under Siege
results.description: Miguel takes on a couple of Public Eyes, but one of them has new SIEGE gear that has been planted to take out Spider-Man.  He's having some difficulty when a mysterious stranger helps him out by blasting the Public Eye.

results.title: Death From On High
results.description: Jordan Boone causes an explosion in the Virtual Unrealty section of Alchemax and Miguel helps rescue him.  Thanatos kidnaps Tyler Stone and Dana, and Miguel convinces him to let Dana go.  They return to the VU section, and release the Prophet.

results.title: Everything is Permitted Nothing is Forbidden... ...In Virtual Unreality
Prophet and Loss
results.description: Spider-Man and Thanatos fight, and are blasted into the warp Jordan has created.  They fight in an unreal world until the Net Prophet pulls Spidey out of it.

results.title: I've come back... ...to clean up Downtown
Boiling Point
results.description: Spider-Man patches up the Net Prophet, then takes him around to see New York.  In the process, they beat up some thugs at Father Jennifer's Cathedral.

results.title: The Rise of the Hammer
results.description: Jordan Boone is in trouble with Alchemax.  But that doesn't matter to Miguel, who is finally reunited with Dana.  They go to visit Alchemax's latest project, Valhalla.  And meet Thor and Heimdall.

results.title: The Fall of the Hammer Part 1 of 5
The Hammer Strikes: Chapter One of The Fall Of The Hammer
results.description: Miguel gets Thor mad and is thrown off the floating city.  He comes back as Spider-Man and fights Thor for awhile.  Gabriel, meanwhile, learns that something is seriously wrong with Miguel's Holo-agent, Lyla.

results.title: Ye Gods
results.description: After the Valhalla mess, Miguel is once again drawn to Downtown, where he finds his mother in a crowd worshipping Thor.  As Miguel, not Spidey, he tricks Bloodsword, who has Thor's Hammer, to get her safely out.

results.title: Blown Circuits
results.description: Lyla goes nuts and tries to kill Dana.  Tyler Stone is nearly killed by his personal assistant, Winston.  Gabriel plugs into the 'net and is immediately attacked.

results.title: School Daze
results.description: Young Miguel O'Hara is personally escorted to his Alchemax sponsered private school by Tyler Stone.

results.title: Meltdown
results.description: Miguel gets Dana out of the apartment only to learn that the whole city has gone nuts.  Something has taken over the central computer network.  Miguel goes to Gabriel's place and finds him plugged in.  He goes into the net after him and meets Discord.

results.title: Orientation
results.description: Before he can even get into his new school, Miguel is drenched by a prankster from an upstairs window.  Angela asks if there is anything he wants, so he asks for a pony.  Kron Stone attacks Angela when she confronts him about the drenching.

results.title: The High Tech Hunt Is On!
Nothing Ventured...
results.description: Miguel learns about his new powers as he escapes Alchemax.  Tyler Stone sends Venture, a professional tracker, after whoever was in the lab.  Rather than let Venture find out who he is, Miguel dresses up and attacks him as Spider-Man.

results.title: Crash and Burn
results.description: Discord threatens Miguel unless he acts as a sidekick.  Miguel agrees after seeing Gabe in the data streams.  With Gabe's help, Miguel destroys Discord.  Gabe then tells Miguel that he knows he's Spider-Man.

results.title: Getting in Deep
results.description: Young Miguel meets Xina, a girl at the school interested in E.T.s.  He agrees to meet her at the pool, but as he is waiting, he is shoved underwater by someone.

results.title: Warning: Don't Get in His Way
Parlor Games
results.description: Three rich girls with expensive armor take on Spider-Man and give him a tough time.

results.title: Did You Just Say...?
results.description: Miguel gets Gabe to look at Lyla and try to fix her.  Kasey  Nash is offered an interesting opportunity by Stark-Fujikawa.

results.title: Dead Boy's Float
results.description: Xina saves Miguel from drowning, and then tries to get him to tell Angela that Kron did it.  Because he's not sure, and he's scared, he doesn't.

results.title: No Fury
results.description: Someone tries to shoot at Spider-Man as he makes his way to Xina's place.  He doesn't know it yet, but Venture's sister, Risque, is after him.  Meanwhile, Kasey Nash is being upgraded by Stark-Fujikawa.  Xina agrees to help Miguel with his holo-agent.

results.title: Visiting Day
results.description: Miguel's parents come to visit.  Miguel's father immediately insults Xina, and Gabriel gets attacked by Kron.  Conchata rescues Gabe, and Kron attacks George, who is about to pound Kron to a pulp when Tyler Stone, Kron's father, shows up.

results.title: Assault and Batteries
results.description: Kasey uses her new powers to attack Alchemax as Payback, only to get creamed by Risque before she can really do anything.  Risque then takes down Spider-Man, and he only defeats her by using his venom to poison her.  Then Venture appears.

results.title: Truth Hurts
results.description: Spider-Man and Venture fight, then Spider-Man goes after Tyler Stone.  Conchata has beat him there, though, and Miguel learns that Tyler Stone is actually his real father.

results.title: For The Little People
results.description: Hulk 2099 gets Draco mad and breaks up with his girl.

results.title: Net Loss
results.description: The Net Prophet wanders through cyberspace, trying to find the keys to his past.  He finds a clue in the form of one Sintilla, but she escapes cyberspace before he can find out more.

results.title: Hostile Takeover
results.description: Miguel tries to deal with the news that Tyler Stone is his father.  Kasey is freed by Stone at Conchata's request.  Miguel throws Dana out of his apartment, and is invited on a road trip by Xina.

results.title: Family Honor
results.description: Tyler insists that George apologize, but Conchata tells him it'll be a cold day in hell before an apology is given.  Tyler backs off, but George thinks she's ruined their lives.  Tyler's wife finds Conchata and tells her that she knows about Miguel.

results.title: Deadly Nightshade
results.description: Xina takes Migual to Nightshade, where their old teacher Angela is working on Genetic manipulation.  While they are there, Alchemax suits attack, intent on a hostile takeover.

results.title: Coming to a Head
results.description: Kron embarrasses Miguel during a soccer game, and Xina suggests to Miguel that he learn to fight back.  Kron attacks Xina while she is helpless in revenge.

results.title: Travesty
results.description: Angela's back-up plan for a hostile takeover happens to have a thing about Spider-Man, and tries to take him out instead of the suits.  Angela is forced to set the self-destruct sequence.  She and Spidey are apparently trapped in the explosion.

results.title: Final Battle
results.description: Kron attacks Xina and Miguel goes to her rescue.  He is cornered by Kron, who has a knife.

results.title: Going Out Of Business Sale
results.description: Scavengers find Angela, dead, and Spider-Man, alive, in the wreckage of Nightshade.  They take Spidey back with them.  Gabe and Kasey run off to Mexico for the day of the dead.  Spidey activates a clone machine in the scavenger's base.

results.title: Brotherly Hate
results.description: Miguel manages to get the knife away from Kron, but is beaten badly.  He is only saved by the timely appearance of Angela, who beats up Kron and informs him that he is expelled.
